    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT : REPORTS OF FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "                ATTENTION: ASSISTANT DIRECTOR D. . . LADD",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "        Colonel [REDACTED], Fourth Air Force, Hamilton Field, California,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "telephonically advised special agent [REDACTED] of the San Francisco",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Office at 10:40 AM on August 27, 1947, that a personal letter had been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "received by his organization from [REDACTED], city editor of the Seattle",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Times, which stated in effect that because there were so many stories going",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "around relative to flying discs and related matters, and that his staff of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "reporters had been attempting to get reliable information concerning such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "stories, he was writing to inquire whether any governmental agency was going  b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "to make an official statement relative to the situation pertaining to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "flying discs; that [REDACTED] also asked whether it would be permissible for",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "his reporters to interview [REDACTED] relative to this situation.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "        Colonel [REDACTED] stated that the above-mentioned letter was answered",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "personally by General [REDACTED] on August 25, 1947, and advised Mr. [REDACTED] that as",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "far as the Army Air Force was concerned, they had no information which would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "definitely clear up the situation; that as far as interviewing persons, Mr.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] could feel free to interview whomsoever he desired, in that there was no b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "censorship at the present time; that in the interest of economy, the Fourth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Air Force headquarters would not run out every lead or report of flying discs,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "but that if well-founded and apparently reliable information were received, that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "such information would be given attention.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "                                                            [unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
